{
  "stem": "1282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But by that time, one of the Hungarian soldiers grabbed me by the neck, pulled me up, and immediately started-- pulled me towards the gate and started searching my pockets.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He finds about six, seven false documents and another one with my picture on it that I'm a Gentile.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what was worse, he finds a letter that a son wrote to his mother that he begged me that I should deliver to his mother who-- who was in that courtyard that-- and I didn't bother reading the letter.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I accepted that I would do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when they opened up the letter, they started reading where this son tells him that he is aware that the Russians are outside and the Hungarians and Germans will be killed in no time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Hungarian-- the Russians, just listen, Mom, to the bombardment of the Russians and just a question of days, so hold out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We will be liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I am OK and you will be liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it gave her encouragement, but blasted away at Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, immediately they knew who I am and what I'm doing, because they knew of us, that we exist.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But occasionally when they caught someone, they shot him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So as they're reading, they started laughing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were taking sort of bets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, whose pigeon is it going to be, because you shoot pigeons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You shoot people like pigeons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Oh, you shot the last one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This is mine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This guy is mine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so-- and-- and I, understanding fluently what they were talking, knew that it's a question of minutes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They would handcuff me, take me to the Danube, probably tie me to somebody else, and shoot me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I faced that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
